{"tid":482423,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"一張圖看出台日男人的「紳士程度」","createTime":"2017-11-28T06:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T16:22:01.000Z","uid":38886,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9ecb47f38b371c4cec22858ed7503fec6e026298","tid":482423,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:57:31.000Z","msg":"本月25、26日間，高雄市最大的同人動漫祭典在駁二藝術特區盛大舉行，為期2天的活動中，上千名民眾和許多攤位擠爆了現場，不僅有許多同人誌社團到場共襄盛舉，還有來自台灣與日本的Cosplayer也來參加，吸引許多動漫迷爭相拍照、大飽眼福。而現場拍照的情況，竟讓一名來自日本的女Coser大感驚訝，並力讚：「台男真的好棒！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/145529_8ff824d278a70dcbe65d27fddb7b7e78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F145529_8ff824d278a70dcbe65d27fddb7b7e78.jpg&h=e4fe3e43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自日本的女Coser石井早苗，活動首日上午就在駁二特區，以可愛性感短裙造型亮相，並接受現場動漫迷的拍照。事後石井也在個人Twitter上PO文，談及她觀察到的台灣拍照文化，力讚台灣民眾在拍攝的禮儀上非常好！<br />\n石井表示，台灣的民眾很紳士，拍攝Coser時的禮儀與水準相當高，不像在日本，大多數的動漫迷都會直接採取「超低角度攝影」，為了捕捉女Coser的裙底風光，甚至不惜躺在地上仰拍，十分誇張。至於台灣，民眾始終都保持與Coser間應有的距離，並且用「正常的角度」拍照，讓她不禁大讚台灣真的好棒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/145640_8b95b57e22608f279afe15dafdab03d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F145640_8b95b57e22608f279afe15dafdab03d4.jpg&h=4b69866d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少網友看了後，也紛紛表示看法，有日本網友也跟著驚訝稱讚：「台灣真的是很有禮貌的國家」；但也有網友表示「其實是這方面文化上的不同」、「台灣人如果那樣做，馬上會被肉搜！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/145656_15a211d9cd18808064c613f25df2a7b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F145656_15a211d9cd18808064c613f25df2a7b6.jpg&h=f2a9bf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/home/張圖看出台日男人的-紳士程度-她讚-台男好棒-041029582.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fhome%2F%E5%BC%B5%E5%9C%96%E7%9C%8B%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%B0%E6%97%A5%E7%94%B7%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84-%E7%B4%B3%E5%A3%AB%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6-%E5%A5%B9%E8%AE%9A-%E5%8F%B0%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%BD%E6%A3%92-041029582.html&d=tcLTG%2BufxrLO4M7QpfdgM6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0d32ecd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/home/張圖看出台日男人的-紳士程度-她讚-台男好棒-041029582.html</a>"},{"pid":"84ae34ecfd26c7189d7a7d3e376f5790251552bc","tid":482423,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1cf7019e07440fe92928459b68d976ec28e973","tid":482423,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6996bb20af5f521afc65fdbcf9554db74d95f7fd","tid":482423,"uid":36157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://photouploads.com/images/71ead5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F71ead5.jpg&h=ed21b54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nmatch"},{"pid":"c157e49d5dbb2ab0fb99d5ca8b4a7db23ab73498","tid":482423,"uid":38886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://photouploads.com/images/71ead5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F71ead5.jpg&h=ed21b54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nmatch</blockquote><br />\n根本就係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2771587d2460ca9795659aefdb0da37426582ca8","tid":482423,"uid":19657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"咩姑咩姑fire<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4fc2817908629458164440402e5b84a1b3a71d","tid":482423,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T13:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>崇日狗仲有咩講